*haskell-platform-2013.2.0.0-r2 (27 Oct 2014)

  27 Oct 2014; Michael Orlitzky <mjo@gentoo.org>
  +haskell-platform-2013.2.0.0-r2.ebuild, -haskell-platform-2013.2.0.0.ebuild:
  Revision bump to fix bug #502146 (thanks to Sean Santos).

  25 Jul 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop redundant '<maintainer>' field, leave only '<herd>'.

*haskell-platform-2013.2.0.0 (26 May 2013)

  26 May 2013; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org>
  +haskell-platform-2013.2.0.0.ebuild:
  Bump haskell-platform to 2013.2.0.0

  09 Feb 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  -haskell-platform-2009.2.0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Removed old.

  29 Dec 2012; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org>
  haskell-platform-2012.2.0.0.ebuild:
  Only list dev-haskell/glut and dev-haskell/opengl deps once in haskell-
  platform-2012.2.0.0 (they were listed twice)

  06 Dec 2012; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  haskell-platform-2009.2.0.2-r1.ebuild:
  Get rid of 'dev-haskell/time' depend as it's a ghc's core library.

